   - You include this license with any redistributed modification.
   - You clearly state that your modification is unofficial and unaffiliated with Maplebox.

2.3 You may create tutorials, showcases, or content featuring the Work (e.g., videos or livestreams), including monetized media content like YouTube videos.

3. RESTRICTIONS

3.1 You may not resell, license, or distribute the original Work or your modifications for any commercial purpose without written permission from Maplebox.

3.2 You may not extract, reuse, or repurpose the assets (e.g., sprites, textures, sound files, maps) for use in other games or projects unless clearly allowed in writing.

3.3 You may not claim the original Work or assets as your own.

3.4 You may not use the Work to train AI models or automated systems, including but not limited to machine learning algorithms, without express written consent.

3.5 You may not use the Work in any way that violates local or international law.

